@vineet-rh Thanks for your contribution. You really need to explain why you want to change this and what the potential consequences are. As you are changing to utcnow, did you test this on a live system in a different timezone? 

Please follow the commit guidelines especially in this area.

(Dont get me wrong, we prefer to run in a different timezone as well - but the utc issue exists for a long time and it is a sensitive area in Airflow)
